text: The E235 series is a train model operated by East Japan Railway Company (JR East) in Japan. The train was made between 2015 and 2017 for the Yamanote Line, and since 2020 for the Yokosuka line. ==Gallery== File:SeriesE235-1000-F01.jpg|Yokosuka Line Variant File:JR East SajaE235-4620 seat 20150419.jpg|Seats Category:Electric multiple units
